      • insertField

        public void insertField(java.lang.String creator,
                        java.lang.String agent,
                        int mu,
                        java.lang.String guid,
                        long timestamp,
                        java.lang.String team,
                        java.lang.String pguid1,
                        long plat1,
                        long plng1,
                        java.lang.String pguid2,
                        long plat2,
                        long plng2,
                        java.lang.String pguid3,
                        long plat3,
                        long plng3,
                        boolean valid)
                 throws EntityDAOException
        Inserts a field into the database. Business logic to check for duplicates and for MU validity should be performed first. Exceptions may occur for duplicate GUID. Invalid MU may cause errors in the fieldProcessing logic. Although fields have point 1, point 2 and point 3 which implies order. No order is a requirement.
        Specified by:
        insertField in interface EntityDAO
        Parameters:
        creator - of the field
        agent - who submitted the field via the field grabber plugin
        mu - of the field
        guid - of the field in string format
        timestamp - of the fields creation time, in milliseconds since epoch (java millis)
        team - of the field. 'E' or 'R'
        pguid1 - guid of the portal for point 1
        plat1 - latitude of the portal for point 1 in E6 format
        plng1 - longitude of the portal for point 1 in E6 format
        pguid2 - guid of the portal for point 2
        plat2 - latitude of the portal for point 2 in E6 format
        plng2 - longitude of the portal for point 2 in E6 format
        pguid3 - guid of the portal for point 3
        plat3 - latitude of the portal for point 3 in E6 format
        plng3 - longitude of the portal for point 3 in E6 format
        Throws:
        EntityDAOException - containing an SQL Exception message
